Incident.Summary: Cybertip 180334030. Suspect IP resolves to Duluth, Georgia.

IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: Attachments -NCMEC Cybertip # }br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--> 180334030 Narrative On 11/27/23, the Maryland State Police Computer Crimes Section /Maryland Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force received NCMEC CyberTip # }br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--> 180334030. The Cyber Tip, generated by Instagram, indicated that a subject uploaded child pornography to the internet. The CyberTip was assigned to Senior Trooper Cooke #6272 for investigation. The CyberTip provided the following information pertaining to the suspect: Name: dani arias Phone: +16785549618 Date of Birth: 08-23-2004 Approximate Age: 19 Screen/User Name: daniela_504amor ESP User ID: 55045290023 IP Address: 2601:c8:8200:51c0:39ed:92a:dd24:ba7 (Login) 11-21-2023 03:06:13 UTC Prior CT Reports: 160064258 Estimated Location: US at 11-24-2023 02:46:58 UTC (Not Verified) Additional Information: PhoneNumberChangeEvent Timestamp: 2023-03-13T16:59:10-07:00 PhoneNumberChangeEvent Timestamp: 2022-08-23T04:35:51-07:00 PhoneNumberChangeEvent Timestamp: 2022-08-23T04:35:48-07:00 DeviceAddedEvent Timestamp: 2022-08-23T04:35:57-07:00 The CyberTip contained 1 reported child pornography file. S/Tpr Cooke reviewed the reported child pornography files and determined that it constitutes child pornography as it is defined under Maryland law. The file is described below: Filename:P1GbZ7yMeZiHWBta404139193_2524560724368266_8421058147289945554_n.mp4 Description: 1 minute video file showing an adult female being vaginally penetrated by a juvenile males penis. The male is reasonably believed to be between 7 - 9 years of age based on lack of development, lack of pubic hair, and overall size compared to the adult female. The CyberTip indicated that the following IP address 2601:c8:8200:51c0:39ed:92a:dd24:ba7 (11-21-2023 03:06:13 UTC) was utilized to upload the reported contraband file. S/T Cooke conducted a query of the upload IP address through an open-source database and determined that it is registered through Comcast Cable and geo-locates generally to Duluth, Georgia. Case Status TRANSFER TO GEORGIA STATE POLICE ICAC
